Subject: [PATCH] PCI: aardvark: Fix masking and unmasking legacy INTx interrupts
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: d212dcee27c1f89517181047e5485fcbba4a25c2
